title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 1 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Oct 1 2022
description:
The Buck Ombudsman segment. Joe Biden couldn't run the neighborhood gas station. Clay wants to invest in Buc-ees gas stations. Morning host Drew Steele of WFSX radio in Fort Myers/Naples gives us an update on Hurricane Ian. C&B take some calls. Biden refuses to call DeSantis about hurricane.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
